Q: How to overcome pride?
<br>A: Pride is a part of ignorance. If we solve one problem, then all the other problems are solved. The main problem is ignorance. If we try to solve one problem at a time, then our whole life will pass away.
<br>Q: What are the best methods for overcoming ignorance?
<br>A: Ignorance is asmita or egoism, &#8220;I am the doer.&#8221; This &#8220;I&#8221; indicates the body. This I-ness is removed by karma yoga. <span class=date>7/6/80</span>
